---

<section class="section contact" id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <hr class="section-rule contact-rule" />
    <div class="contact-inner reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">04 — Contact</p>
      <h2 class="contact-title">Let's build<em>.</em></h2>
      <p class="contact-lede">
        Tell us what you're trying to make possible. We'll reply with a point of view — and if
        we're not the right fit, we'll say so.
      </p>
      <div class="contact-actions">
        <a href="mailto:contact@siliconsteelsoftware.com" class="btn btn-primary">
          contact@siliconsteelsoftware.com
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/silicon-steel-software"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-link"
        >
          LinkedIn
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M7 7h10v10" /><path d="M7 17 17 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-rule {
    border-top-color: var(--rule-dark);
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
  }

  .contact-inner {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    justify-items: start;
  }

  .contact-title {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
  }

  .contact-title em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .contact-lede {
    max-width: 36rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .contact-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
